WHAT ARE CHIPSET MOTHERBOARD & ORGINAL MOTHEBOARD? \par
\par
ORIGINAL MOTHERBOARD-THE CHIPSET (NORTH BRIDGE+SOUTH BRIDGE) AND THE MOTHERBOARD ARE MANUFACTURED BY SAME COMPANY LIKE INTEL \par
\par
EXAMPLE INTEL ORIGINAL MOTHERBOARD \par
\par
CHIPSET MOTHERBOARD-THE CHIPSET AND MOTHERBOARD ARE MANUFACTURED BY DIFFERENT VENDOR OR COMPANY. \par
\par
LIKE GIGABYTE BOARD WITH INTEL CHIPSET OR ASUS MOTHERBOARD WITH INTEL CHIPSET. \par
\par
WHAT IS CHIPSET? \par
\par
COMBINATION OF MULTIPLE CHIPS.EXAMPLE -NORTH BRIDGE & SOUTH BRIDGE \par
\par
NORTH BRIDGE/GMCH-GRAPHICS MEMORY CONTROLLER HUB>ITS CONTROL ONBOARD GRAPHICS OR GRAPHICS CARD(AGP/PCIE) AND MEMORY PART (RAM) \par
\par
AGP-ACCELERATED GRAPHICS PORT \par
\par
PCIE-PERIPHERAL COMPONENT INTERCONNECT EXPRESS \par
\par
OR \par
\par
PCIE-PERIPHERAL COMPONENT INTERFACE EXPRESS \par
\par
SOUTH BRIDGE OR IOCH (INPUT OUTPUT CONTROLLER HUB)==>USED TO CONTROL 1/0 \par
PERIPHERAL EXCEPT SERIAL PORT, PARALLEL PORT, AND FLOPPY CONTROLLER\par
==================================================================================================\par
SUPER 1/0 IC==>USED TO CONTROL SERIAL PARALLEL AND FLOPPY CONTROLLER \par
==================================================================================================\par
LPC IC (LOW PIN COUNT) ==>USED TO CONTROL SERIAL PARALLEL AND FLOPPY CONTROLLER. IN OLDER MOTHERBOARD IT WAS USED IN PLACE OF SUPER IO IC. \par
\par
RTC IC==REAL TIME CLOCK (ICS MANUFATURER THIS IC AND A PIEZOELECTRONICS CRYSTAL IS PRESENT NEAR IT. \par
\par
IT WILL GENERATE CLOCK PULSE \par
\par
1.IT IS THE MAIN DRIVING FORCE IN COMPUTER \par
2.IT IS USED TO SYNCHRONIZED ALL FUNCTION OF THE COMPUTER \par
======================================================================================================\par
PROCESSOR SOCKET \par
i) LGA-LAND GRID ARRAY-->MALE SOCKET-->HAVING PINS--RECENT SOCKET-->USED TO CONNECT INTEL CORE 13/15/17/19 PROCESSOR \par
ii) PGA-PIN GRID ARRAY-->FEMALE SOCKET-->HAVING HOLES-->USED TO CONNECT OLD/NEW PROCESSOR LIKE AMD ATHLON/PHENOM/FX/RYZEN \par
=======================================================================================================\par
WHAT IS VRM ? \par
VOLTAGE REGULATOR MODULE---USED TO REGULATE THE PROCESSOR VOLTAGE. \par
=======================================================================================================\par
